title: Salad Days
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Owner offers a lay-out of freshly bought ingredients to have in your salad or wrap, which are ample in size. Vegan ingredients are eggplant hummus, spinach, mushrooms, couscous, chickpeas, lentils, black beans, green and black olives, avocado, cucumber, tomatoes, asparagus, vinaigrette salad dressing and hot sauce. Located in a hallway in Cumberland Terrace.
